  "prompt": "How do I get the permission for taking photos at theosophical society, adayar, Chennai?",
  "response": "To get permission for taking photos at the Theosophical Society in Adyar, Chennai, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. Contact the Administration:\n- Visit the Theosophical Society headquarters in Adyar\n- Speak with the administrative office\n- Request permission for photography\n\n2. Required Documentation:\n- Carry a valid photo ID\n- Explain the purpose of photography (personal, professional, etc.)\n\n3. Potential Contact Details:\n- Phone: +91-44-2491 1198\n- Email: tsadyar@gmail.com\n- Website: www.ts-adyar.org\n\n4. Photography Guidelines:\n- Some areas might have restrictions\n- Professional or commercial photography may require additional permissions\n- Respect the sanctity of the campus\n\n5. Possible Fees:\n- There might be a nominal fee for photography permissions\n- Confirm details during your inquiry\n\n6. Best Time to Visit:\n- During office hours\n- Preferably contact in advance\n\nTip: Be polite, explain your purpose clearly, and follow their guidelines for a smooth permission process.\n\nRemember that specific requirements might change, so it's best to contact them directly for the most current information.",
